hi guys this is how to add bones on altar :)
first goto itemonobject in your source open it then paste this in it:
[code]            case 409:
                if (itemId == 536) { //dragon bones pray
                    Engine.playerItems.deleteItem(player, 536, Engine.playerItems.getItemSlot(player, 536), 1);
                    player.requestAnim(713, 0);
                    player.requestGFX(520, 2);
                    player.appendExperience(7000, 5);
                    player.getActionSender().sendMessage(player, "You give the bones as in a sacrifice to (your name here).");
                }
                break;
[/code]
save, compile, run, spawn bones and use them on altar :)
